{"parentUuid":"d35731f8-5d75-4133-ad30-2f0903678e0d","isSidechain":true,"agentId":"aba4c59c369d45698","message":{"model":"claude-opus-4-8","id":"msg_01RvGurXeD2MNPYhZk6hwcCL","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"tool_use","id":"toolu_01Dxv4Ydkk7R8WhgfZfoMHfB","name":"WebSearch","input":{"query":"AlphaEvolve white paper architecture Gemini Flash Pro ensemble evolutionary"},"caller":{"type":"direct"}}],"stop_reason":"tool_use","stop_sequence":null,"stop_details":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1003,"cache_creation_input_tokens":5757,"cache_read_input_tokens":6425,"output_tokens":150,"server_tool_use":{"web_search_requests":0,"web_fetch_requests":0},"service_tier":"standard","cache_creation":{"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":5757},"inference_geo":"not_available","iterations":[{"input_tokens":1003,"output_tokens":150,"cache_read_input_tokens":6425,"cache_creation_input_tokens":5757,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":5757,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0},"type":"message"}],"speed":"standard"},"diagnostics":{"cache_miss_reason":{"type":"tools_changed","cache_missed_input_tokens":8111}}},"requestId":"req_011CcG23xnX3efpf651YkjHj","attributionAgent":"general-purpose","attributionSkill":"deep-research","type":"assistant","uuid":"41c08ff2-100a-49b9-98c4-b72b874baa52","timestamp":"2026-06-21T07:34:46.793Z","userType":"external","entrypoint":"cli","cwd":"/Users/gg/Work/Yogi","sessionId":"d8d6b712-ec33-4776-a194-d9a72216a25f","version":"2.1.183","gitBranch":"main","slug":"bright-wondering-lantern"}
{"parentUuid":"d35731f8-5d75-4133-ad30-2f0903678e0d","isSidechain":true,"promptId":"dcbe4efb-6e32-4db6-a75a-aa49b911d737","agentId":"aba4c59c369d45698","type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_014Qtijidtjy9HhoZ446sPSu","type":"tool_result","content":"Web search results for query: \"AlphaEvolve a Gemini-powered coding agent deepmind\"\n\nLinks: [{\"title\":\"AlphaEvolve: Gemini-powered coding agent scaling impact across fields — Google DeepMind\",\"url\":\"https://deepmind.google/blog/alphaevolve-impact/\"},{\"title\":\"AlphaEvolve: A Gemini-powered coding agent for designing advanced algorithms — Google DeepMind\",\"url\":\"https://deepmind.google/blog/alphaevolve-a-gemini-powered-coding-agent-for-designing-advanced-algorithms/\"},{\"title\":\"AlphaEvolve: A coding agent for scientific and algorithmic discovery\",\"url\":\"https://storage.googleapis.com/deepmind-media/DeepMind.com/Blog/alphaevolve-a-gemini-powered-coding-agent-for-designing-advanced-algorithms/AlphaEvolve.pdf\"},{\"title\":\"AlphaEvolve - Wikipedia\",\"url\":\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/AlphaEvolve\"},{\"title\":\"AlphaEvolve: How DeepMind’s Gemini-Powered Agent Is Evolving the Future of Code | by Micheal Lanham | Medium\",\"url\":\"https://medium.com/@Micheal-Lanham/alphaevolve-how-deepminds-gemini-powered-agent-is-evolving-the-future-of-code-f48075505bb6\"},{\"title\":\"Meet AlphaEvolve, the Google AI that writes its own code—and just saved millions in computing costs | VentureBeat\",\"url\":\"https://venturebeat.com/ai/meet-alphaevolve-the-google-ai-that-writes-its-own-code-and-just-saved-millions-in-computing-costs\"},{\"title\":\"AlphaEvolve: Gemini-Powered AI Coding Agent and the Evolution of AI-Designed Algorithms | by Ashish Chadha | Medium\",\"url\":\"https://ashishchadha11944.medium.com/alphaevolve-gemini-powered-ai-coding-agent-and-the-evolution-of-ai-designed-algorithms-e2733b84043d\"},{\"title\":\"AlphaEvolve - AI Powered Coding Agent For Designing Algorithms\",\"url\":\"https://alphaevolveai.dev/\"},{\"title\":\"AlphaEvolve: A Gemini-powered coding agent for designing advanced algorithms - Google DeepMind - Michael Bargury\",\"url\":\"https://www.mbgsec.com/archive/2025-07-20-alphaevolve-a-gemini-powered-coding-agent-for-designing-advanced-algorithms-google-deepmind/\"}]\n\nBased on the search results, here's what I found about AlphaEvolve:\n\n## Overview\n\nAlphaEvolve is a Gemini-powered coding agent for designing advanced algorithms. It was developed by Google DeepMind and unveiled in May 2025.\n\n## How It Works\n\nAlphaEvolve pairs the creative problem-solving capabilities of Gemini models with automated evaluators that verify answers, and uses an evolutionary framework to improve upon the most promising ideas. AlphaEvolve leverages an ensemble of state-of-the-art large language models: Gemini Flash maximizes the breadth of ideas explored, while Gemini Pro provides critical depth with insightful suggestions.\n\n## Key Achievements\n\nAlphaEvolve has demonstrated significant impact across multiple domains:\n\n- **Data Centers & Chip Design**: AlphaEvolve enhanced the efficiency of Google's data centers, chip design and AI training processes. AlphaEvolve achieved up to a 32.5% speedup for the FlashAttention kernel implementation in Transformer-based AI models.\n\n- **Mathematical Discoveries**: One discovery toppled a mathematical record that had stood for 56 years, with AlphaEvolve finding an algorithm that surpasses Strassen's algorithm from 1969 for the first time in that setting.\n\n- **Grid Optimization**: AlphaEvolve helped increase the ability of a trained Graph Neural Network model to find feasible solutions for the AC Optimal Power Flow problem from 14% to over 88%.\n\n## Design Advantages\n\nAlphaEvolve's solution offers significant operational advantages of human-readable code: interpretability, debuggability, predictability and ease of deployment.\n\n\nREMINDER: You MUST include the sources above in your response to the user using markdown hyperlinks."}]},"uuid":"d4bbd3c3-ffb9-4e48-83d8-e096561c37ed","timestamp":"2026-06-21T07:34:53.663Z","toolUseResult":{"query":"AlphaEvolve a Gemini-powered coding agent deepmind","results":[{"tool_use_id":"srvtoolu_01YEAqNn2dF6BwiRxkUH8jCQ","content":[{"title":"AlphaEvolve: Gemini-powered coding agent scaling impact across fields — Google DeepMind","url":"https://deepmind.google/blog/alphaevolve-impact/"},{"title":"AlphaEvolve: A Gemini-powered coding agent for designing advanced algorithms — Google DeepMind","url":"https://deepmind.google/blog/alphaevolve-a-gemini-powered-coding-agent-for-designing-advanced-algorithms/"},{"title":"AlphaEvolve: A coding agent for scientific and algorithmic discovery","url":"https://storage.googleapis.com/deepmind-media/DeepMind.com/Blog/alphaevolve-a-gemini-powered-coding-agent-for-designing-advanced-algorithms/AlphaEvolve.pdf"},{"title":"AlphaEvolve - Wikipedia","url":"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/AlphaEvolve"},{"title":"AlphaEvolve: How DeepMind’s Gemini-Powered Agent Is Evolving the Future of Code | by Micheal Lanham | Medium","url":"https://medium.com/@Micheal-Lanham/alphaevolve-how-deepminds-gemini-powered-agent-is-evolving-the-future-of-code-f48075505bb6"},{"title":"Meet AlphaEvolve, the Google AI that writes its own code—and just saved millions in computing costs | VentureBeat","url":"https://venturebeat.com/ai/meet-alphaevolve-the-google-ai-that-writes-its-own-code-and-just-saved-millions-in-computing-costs"},{"title":"AlphaEvolve: Gemini-Powered AI Coding Agent and the Evolution of AI-Designed Algorithms | by Ashish Chadha | Medium","url":"https://ashishchadha11944.medium.com/alphaevolve-gemini-powered-ai-coding-agent-and-the-evolution-of-ai-designed-algorithms-e2733b84043d"},{"title":"AlphaEvolve - AI Powered Coding Agent For Designing Algorithms","url":"https://alphaevolveai.dev/"},{"title":"AlphaEvolve: A Gemini-powered coding agent for designing advanced algorithms - Google DeepMind - Michael Bargury","url":"https://www.mbgsec.com/archive/2025-07-20-alphaevolve-a-gemini-powered-coding-agent-for-designing-advanced-algorithms-google-deepmind/"}]},"Based on the search results, here's what I found about AlphaEvolve:\n\n## Overview\n\nAlphaEvolve is a Gemini-powered coding agent for designing advanced algorithms. It was developed by Google DeepMind and unveiled in May 2025.\n\n## How It Works\n\nAlphaEvolve pairs the creative problem-solving capabilities of Gemini models with automated evaluators that verify answers, and uses an evolutionary framework to improve upon the most promising ideas. AlphaEvolve leverages an ensemble of state-of-the-art large language models: Gemini Flash maximizes the breadth of ideas explored, while Gemini Pro provides critical depth with insightful suggestions.\n\n## Key Achievements\n\nAlphaEvolve has demonstrated significant impact across multiple domains:\n\n- **Data Centers & Chip Design**: AlphaEvolve enhanced the efficiency of Google's data centers, chip design and AI training processes. AlphaEvolve achieved up to a 32.5% speedup for the FlashAttention kernel implementation in Transformer-based AI models.\n\n- **Mathematical Discoveries**: One discovery toppled a mathematical record that had stood for 56 years, with AlphaEvolve finding an algorithm that surpasses Strassen's algorithm from 1969 for the first time in that setting.\n\n- **Grid Optimization**: AlphaEvolve helped increase the ability of a trained Graph Neural Network model to find feasible solutions for the AC Optimal Power Flow problem from 14% to over 88%.\n\n## Design Advantages\n\nAlphaEvolve's solution offers significant operational advantages of human-readable code: interpretability, debuggability, predictability and ease of deployment."],"durationSeconds":6.871612165998667,"searchCount":1},"sourceToolAssistantUUID":"d35731f8-5d75-4133-ad30-2f0903678e0d","userType":"external","entrypoint":"cli","cwd":"/Users/gg/Work/Yogi","sessionId":"d8d6b712-ec33-4776-a194-d9a72216a25f","version":"2.1.183","gitBranch":"main","slug":"bright-wondering-lantern"}
{"parentUuid":"41c08ff2-100a-49b9-98c4-b72b874baa52","isSidechain":true,"promptId":"dcbe4efb-6e32-4db6-a75a-aa49b911d737","agentId":"aba4c59c369d45698","type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_01Dxv4Ydkk7R8WhgfZfoMHfB","type":"tool_result","content":"Web search results for query: \"AlphaEvolve white paper architecture Gemini Flash Pro ensemble evolutionary\"\n\nLinks: [{\"title\":\"(PDF) AlphaEvolve: A coding agent for scientific and algorithmic discovery\",\"url\":\"https://www.researchgate.net/publication/392736011_AlphaEvolve_A_coding_agent_for_scientific_and_algorithmic_discovery\"},{\"title\":\"AlphaEvolve: A coding agent for scientific and algorithmic discovery\",\"url\":\"https://storage.googleapis.com/deepmind-media/DeepMind.com/Blog/alphaevolve-a-gemini-powered-coding-agent-for-designing-advanced-algorithms/AlphaEvolve.pdf\"},{\"title\":\"AlphaEvolve - by Grigory Sapunov - Gonzo ML - Substack\",\"url\":\"https://gonzoml.substack.com/p/alphaevolve\"},{\"title\":\"Google DeepMind Unveils AI Coding Agent AlphaEvolve - InfoQ\",\"url\":\"https://www.infoq.com/news/2025/05/google-alpha-evolve/\"},{\"title\":\"AlphaEvolve: Evolutionary agent from DeepMind - Composio\",\"url\":\"https://composio.dev/blog/alphaevolve-evolutionary-agent-from-deepmind\"},{\"title\":\"Google DeepMind’s AlphaEvolve: A Breakthrough AI Coding Agent | SSOJet - Enterprise SSO & Identity Solutions\",\"url\":\"https://ssojet.com/blog/google-deepminds-alphaevolve-a-breakthrough-ai-coding-agent\"},{\"title\":\"Overcoming LLM Performance Plateau: AlphaEvolve’s Evolutionary Approach to Continuous Gemini Enhancement | by Kishore Gopalan | Google Cloud - Community | Medium\",\"url\":\"https://medium.com/google-cloud/overcoming-llm-performance-plateau-alphaevolves-evolutionary-approach-to-continuous-gemini-e5a22c64b540\"},{\"title\":\"AlphaEvolve on Google Cloud | Google Cloud Blog\",\"url\":\"https://cloud.google.com/blog/products/ai-machine-learning/alphaevolve-on-google-cloud/\"},{\"title\":\"AlphaEvolve: A Gemini-powered coding agent for designing advanced algorithms — Google DeepMind\",\"url\":\"https://deepmind.google/blog/alphaevolve-a-gemini-powered-coding-agent-for-designing-advanced-algorithms/\"},{\"title\":\"GitHub - algorithmicsuperintelligence/openevolve: Open-source implementation of AlphaEvolve · GitHub\",\"url\":\"https://github.com/algorithmicsuperintelligence/openevolve\"}]\n\nI found comprehensive information about AlphaEvolve from the white paper and related sources. Here are the key details about its architecture and ensemble approach:\n\n## Overview\n\nAlphaEvolve is an evolutionary coding agent that substantially enhances capabilities of state-of-the-art LLMs on highly challenging tasks such as tackling open scientific problems or optimizing critical pieces of computational infrastructure.\n\n## Architecture & Ensemble Approach\n\nAlphaEvolve employs an ensemble of large language models, specifically utilizing a combination of Gemini 2.0 Flash and Gemini 2.0 Pro. This ensemble approach allows balancing computational throughput with the quality of generated solutions—Gemini 2.0 Flash, with its lower latency, enables a higher rate of candidate generation, while Gemini 2.0 Pro, possessing greater capabilities, provides occasional, higher-quality suggestions that can significantly advance the evolutionary search.\n\n## Evolutionary Pipeline\n\nAlphaEvolve orchestrates an autonomous pipeline of LLMs, whose task is to improve an algorithm by making direct changes to the code. The system operates through a cyclical pipeline that combines LLM-driven code generation with an evolutionary strategy by sampling \"parent\" programs from a database and having an ensemble of Gemini models generate new algorithmic solutions or propose modifications using a \"diff-based\" mutation strategy.\n\n## Real-World Applications\n\nAlphaEvolve improved kernel tiling and FlashAttention operations in AI training processes, resulting in 23% and 32% speedup respectively. Google was able to recover 0.7% of its worldwide compute resources through a solution AlphaEvolve developed for the Borg task orchestrator.\n\n\nREMINDER: You MUST include the sources above in your response to the user using markdown hyperlinks."}]},"uuid":"2d34af8e-8624-42b8-963f-86972a7b0637","timestamp":"2026-06-21T07:34:58.773Z","toolUseResult":{"query":"AlphaEvolve white paper architecture Gemini Flash Pro ensemble evolutionary","results":[{"tool_use_id":"srvtoolu_01KCtCH7E4YHxGf6NKfUz5cj","content":[{"title":"(PDF) AlphaEvolve: A coding agent for scientific and algorithmic discovery","url":"https://www.researchgate.net/publication/392736011_AlphaEvolve_A_coding_agent_for_scientific_and_algorithmic_discovery"},{"title":"AlphaEvolve: A coding agent for scientific and algorithmic discovery","url":"https://storage.googleapis.com/deepmind-media/DeepMind.com/Blog/alphaevolve-a-gemini-powered-coding-agent-for-designing-advanced-algorithms/AlphaEvolve.pdf"},{"title":"AlphaEvolve - by Grigory Sapunov - Gonzo ML - Substack","url":"https://gonzoml.substack.com/p/alphaevolve"},{"title":"Google DeepMind Unveils AI Coding Agent AlphaEvolve - InfoQ","url":"https://www.infoq.com/news/2025/05/google-alpha-evolve/"},{"title":"AlphaEvolve: Evolutionary agent from DeepMind - Composio","url":"https://composio.dev/blog/alphaevolve-evolutionary-agent-from-deepmind"},{"title":"Google DeepMind’s AlphaEvolve: A Breakthrough AI Coding Agent | SSOJet - Enterprise SSO & Identity Solutions","url":"https://ssojet.com/blog/google-deepminds-alphaevolve-a-breakthrough-ai-coding-agent"},{"title":"Overcoming LLM Performance Plateau: AlphaEvolve’s Evolutionary Approach to Continuous Gemini Enhancement | by Kishore Gopalan | Google Cloud - Community | Medium","url":"https://medium.com/google-cloud/overcoming-llm-performance-plateau-alphaevolves-evolutionary-approach-to-continuous-gemini-e5a22c64b540"},{"title":"AlphaEvolve on Google Cloud | Google Cloud Blog","url":"https://cloud.google.com/blog/products/ai-machine-learning/alphaevolve-on-google-cloud/"},{"title":"AlphaEvolve: A Gemini-powered coding agent for designing advanced algorithms — Google DeepMind","url":"https://deepmind.google/blog/alphaevolve-a-gemini-powered-coding-agent-for-designing-advanced-algorithms/"},{"title":"GitHub - algorithmicsuperintelligence/openevolve: Open-source implementation of AlphaEvolve · GitHub","url":"https://github.com/algorithmicsuperintelligence/openevolve"}]},"I found comprehensive information about AlphaEvolve from the white paper and related sources. Here are the key details about its architecture and ensemble approach:\n\n## Overview\n\nAlphaEvolve is an evolutionary coding agent that substantially enhances capabilities of state-of-the-art LLMs on highly challenging tasks such as tackling open scientific problems or optimizing critical pieces of computational infrastructure.\n\n## Architecture & Ensemble Approach\n\nAlphaEvolve employs an ensemble of large language models, specifically utilizing a combination of Gemini 2.0 Flash and Gemini 2.0 Pro. This ensemble approach allows balancing computational throughput with the quality of generated solutions—Gemini 2.0 Flash, with its lower latency, enables a higher rate of candidate generation, while Gemini 2.0 Pro, possessing greater capabilities, provides occasional, higher-quality suggestions that can significantly advance the evolutionary search.\n\n## Evolutionary Pipeline\n\nAlphaEvolve orchestrates an autonomous pipeline of LLMs, whose task is to improve an algorithm by making direct changes to the code. The system operates through a cyclical pipeline that combines LLM-driven code generation with an evolutionary strategy by sampling \"parent\" programs from a database and having an ensemble of Gemini models generate new algorithmic solutions or propose modifications using a \"diff-based\" mutation strategy.\n\n## Real-World Applications\n\nAlphaEvolve improved kernel tiling and FlashAttention operations in AI training processes, resulting in 23% and 32% speedup respectively. Google was able to recover 0.7% of its worldwide compute resources through a solution AlphaEvolve developed for the Borg task orchestrator."],"durationSeconds":11.21452845899947,"searchCount":1},"sourceToolAssistantUUID":"41c08ff2-100a-49b9-98c4-b72b874baa52","userType":"external","entrypoint":"cli","cwd":"/Users/gg/Work/Yogi","sessionId":"d8d6b712-ec33-4776-a194-d9a72216a25f","version":"2.1.183","gitBranch":"main","slug":"bright-wondering-lantern"}
