{"parentUuid":"db4bee06-34ba-4d8a-9740-0cbf367ff6ed","isSidechain":true,"promptId":"dcbe4efb-6e32-4db6-a75a-aa49b911d737","agentId":"aba4c59c369d45698","type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_01M5M6jUdKb2zfxCyAAWmu7G","type":"tool_result","content":"# AlphaEvolve's Architecture: Key Components\n\n## The Ensemble Approach\n\n**Gemini Models Used:**\n\"AlphaEvolve leverages an ensemble of state-of-the-art large language models: our fastest and most efficient model, Gemini Flash... while our most powerful model, Gemini Pro...\"\n\n**Division of Labor:**\nFlash maximizes \"the breadth of ideas explored, while our most powerful model, Gemini Pro, provides critical depth with insightful suggestions.\"\n\n## The Evolutionary Loop\n\nThe system operates through a cycle combining creative and evaluative processes:\n\n1. **Code Generation**: \"Together, these models propose computer programs that implement algorithmic solutions as code.\"\n\n2. **Verification and Scoring**: \"AlphaEvolve verifies, runs and scores the proposed programs using automated evaluation metrics.\"\n\n3. **Population Management**: A \"programs database\" stores candidates and \"implements an evolutionary algorithm that determines which programs will be used for future prompts.\"\n\n## Code Modification Scope\n\nThe document indicates AlphaEvolve works at multiple levels—from individual functions to comprehensive rewrites. It discovered \"a novel gradient-based optimization procedure\" with \"extensive changes across several components,\" demonstrating capability beyond isolated function edits to broader algorithmic redesign.\n\nThe exact mechanisms for code-level edits (diffs vs. full rewrites) aren't explicitly detailed in the provided content."}]},"uuid":"a0a5490a-3bb6-4328-916a-d5c9b70b4dfb","timestamp":"2026-06-21T07:35:09.511Z","toolUseResult":{"bytes":151623,"code":200,"codeText":"OK","result":"# AlphaEvolve's Architecture: Key Components\n\n## The Ensemble Approach\n\n**Gemini Models Used:**\n\"AlphaEvolve leverages an ensemble of state-of-the-art large language models: our fastest and most efficient model, Gemini Flash... while our most powerful model, Gemini Pro...\"\n\n**Division of Labor:**\nFlash maximizes \"the breadth of ideas explored, while our most powerful model, Gemini Pro, provides critical depth with insightful suggestions.\"\n\n## The Evolutionary Loop\n\nThe system operates through a cycle combining creative and evaluative processes:\n\n1. **Code Generation**: \"Together, these models propose computer programs that implement algorithmic solutions as code.\"\n\n2. **Verification and Scoring**: \"AlphaEvolve verifies, runs and scores the proposed programs using automated evaluation metrics.\"\n\n3. **Population Management**: A \"programs database\" stores candidates and \"implements an evolutionary algorithm that determines which programs will be used for future prompts.\"\n\n## Code Modification Scope\n\nThe document indicates AlphaEvolve works at multiple levels—from individual functions to comprehensive rewrites. It discovered \"a novel gradient-based optimization procedure\" with \"extensive changes across several components,\" demonstrating capability beyond isolated function edits to broader algorithmic redesign.\n\nThe exact mechanisms for code-level edits (diffs vs. full rewrites) aren't explicitly detailed in the provided content.","durationMs":4739,"url":"https://deepmind.google/blog/alphaevolve-a-gemini-powered-coding-agent-for-designing-advanced-algorithms/"},"sourceToolAssistantUUID":"db4bee06-34ba-4d8a-9740-0cbf367ff6ed","userType":"external","entrypoint":"cli","cwd":"/Users/gg/Work/Yogi","sessionId":"d8d6b712-ec33-4776-a194-d9a72216a25f","version":"2.1.183","gitBranch":"main","slug":"bright-wondering-lantern"}
